  "body": "# Bug Report\r\nCommunity chats unreact counter badge seems to have a very light version of the blue background color. Reproducible only on android\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nhttps://www.figma.com/file/h9wo4GipgZURbqqr1vShFN/Communities-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=5040%3A188714&mode=design&t=thINoDvjW1LlxNlE-1\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n<img src=\"https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/assets/28704507/95f8a2fe-47a7-4a73-823a-fe76c7a235fe\" height=\"350\">\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n\r\n1) Open Status\r\n2) User A and B join the same community\r\n3) User A sends message in the general channel\r\n4) User B replies the User A message\r\n5) Check unread counter badge on User A device\r\n6) Notice the background color is different from the expected\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status version: nightly \r\n- Operating System: Android, iOS\r\n",
